summary: This textile's image is river. Inspiration from "方丈記（Hojoki）". 「ゆく河の流れは絶えずして、しかももとの水にあらず。淀みに浮かぶうたかたは、かつ消えかつ結びて、久しくとどまりたるためしなし。」...
caption:
This textile’s image is river. Inspiration from “方丈記（Hojoki）”.

「ゆく河の流れは絶えずして、しかももとの水にあらず。淀みに浮かぶうたかたは、かつ消えかつ結びて、久しくとどまりたるためしなし。」

“The flowing river never stops and yet the water never stays the same.
Foam floats upon the pools, scattering, re-forming, never lingering long.”

summary: BEEF COMMISSIONS OPEN!
title: BEEF COMMISSIONS OPEN!
body:
Hey! The name’s Beef and I draw stuff! I’m trying to get as prepared for college as possible for this fall, and commissions will super help out! All the information is listed below! If you’re interested all you have to do is dm me here! I’ll do just about anything, just make sure it follows the rules below:

I WILL NOT DRAW:

-ns/fw

-intense gore

-nu/dity

-heavy machinery

-anything even remotely pedophilic/incestuous/gross in nature

I WILL DRAW:

-original characters!

-furries!

-fanart! (Preferably something I’m familiar with, but I’m flexible)

-creatures!

-mild injuries/blood!

-cute, fluffy things!

-sad, angsty things!

-body horror within reason!

PRICING:

Icons:

-Lineart: $10 +5ph (per hour)

-Colors: $15 +5ph

-Background and/or shading: $20 +5ph

Busts:

-Sketch: $20 +10ph

-Sketch+color: $25 +10ph

-Lineart: $25 +10ph

-Color: $30 +10ph

-Background and/or Shading: $35 +10ph

Midbody:

-Sketch: $25 +15ph

-Sketch+color: $30 +15ph

-Lineart: $30 +15ph

-Color: $35 +15ph

-Minor Background and/or shading: $40 +15ph

-Detailed Background: $45 +15ph

Fullbody:

-Sketch: $30 +20ph

-Sketch + color (example not given): $35 +20ph

-Lineart: $35 +20ph

-Color: $40 +20ph

-Minor Background and/or shading: $45 +20ph

-Detailed Background: $50 +20ph

HOW TO DO THIS THING:

DM me over tumblr through this blog and let me know what you want. Be as specific as possible. If you want an oc/creature/fandom character I don’t know about, please provide a reference! 

After I get started I will update you with screenshots– don’t be afraid to ask! Anything more than a sketch, I will ask for the flat rate up front. You will get a refund if I, for some reason, am unable to finish the commission, (though I imagine that won’t be an issue) or if you are utterly unhappy with the product. Payment through paypal invoices only! :D 

If you have any questions don’t be afraid to ask! Also whether I post your commission or not is entirely up to you just lmk!

IF YOU WANT MORE THAN ONE CHARACTER PER PIECE:

The price will be the Final Price with an added fee of half the Final Price. So if your SKETCH BUST ends up costing $30, with an added character that would be $45.

–Anywho, long post aside, thanks for supporting me! Even if it’s just been through following me or whatever, my journey as an artist on the internet has been a wild ride and I can’t wait to see where this new step will take me! <3
